text: "SpongeBob's Big Birthday Blowout" is an episode in season 12 of SpongeBob SquarePants. In the episode, SpongeBob celebrates his 20th anniversary. It first aired on July 12, 2019. == References == Category:SpongeBob SquarePants episodes Category:2019 television episodes Category:Television episodes about birthdays
